1.5T MRI Scan Information

Source: R/data.R
MRIMETA.Rd

1.5T MRI Scan Information data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(MRIMETA)

Format

A data frame with 4740 observations and 36 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3

  • COLPROT factor Study protocol of data collection , with levels: ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2, ADNI3, ADNI4

  • PTID character Participant ID

  • RID numeric Participant roster ID Range value: 2, ..., 6837

  • VISCODE character Visit code

  • VISCODE2 character Translated visit code

  • EXAMDATE Scan Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • FIELD_STRENGTH character Field Strength

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO: 1.5T=1.5 Tesla

    • ADNI2, ADNI3: 1.5T=1.5 Tesla ; 3T=3 Tesla

    • ADNI4: 3T=3 Tesla

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • RECNO character 1=Original Scan ; 2=Rescan Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMCONDCT character Was the scan conducted?

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMREASON character If No, please provide reason why the scan was not conducted: 1=Illness ; 2=Participant unavailable ; 3=Participant unwilling ; 4=Administrative problems ; 5=Withdrawn consent ; 6=Other (specify) Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMSCOUT character 1. Tri-Planar Scout (if available, otherwise use an axial scout) 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMSMPRAGE character 2. Straight Sagittal MPRAGE Sequence 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMRMPRAGE character 3. Repeat Straight Sagittal MPRAGE Sequence 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMB1HEAD character 4. B1 Calibration Head Coil Scan (Only applicable for phased array head coil on GE and Siemens systems) 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMB1BODY character 5. B1 Calibration Body Coil Scan (Only applicable for phased array head coil on GE and Siemens systems) 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMECHO character 6. Straight Axial Fast or Turbo Spin Echo 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMPHAN character 7. In new exam; Perform ADNI QC Scan. Localizer and Straight Sagittal MPRAGE (with increased slice thickness to ensure phantom coverage) 1=Yes ; 0=No Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMTRNSFR character Was data transferred to LONI within 24 hours of scan?

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMTRNDATE character Transfer Date

  • MMTRNDATEYR_DRVD numeric Transfer Year (Derived from MMTRNDATE) Range value: 2005, ..., 2023

  • MMARCHIVE character Data Archived Locally

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMLPDONE character Was a Lumbar Puncture completed prior to the MRI scan?

    • ADNI1, ADNIGO, ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MMLPINTER character If Yes, What was the interval between LP and MRI? 1=less than 6 hours ; 2=6-12 hours ; 3=13-24 hours ; 4=25-48 hours ; 5=49-72 hours ; 6=more than 72 hours Decoded Value: Yes

  • SEDATIVE character Was sedation medication consumed for use during MRI scan?

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • OTRDEV character Other Protocol Variations

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MOTION character Patient Motion Problems:

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • EYEKEEP character Did the participant keep their eyes open (MRI Tech: ask the subject right after the scan)

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No ; 2=N/A Scanner manufacturer is GE

    • ADNI3: 0=No ; 1=Yes ; 2=N/A Scanner manufacturer is GE

    • ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • EYEASK character Was the participant instructed to open their eyes?

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No ; 2=N/A Scanner manufacturer is GE

    • ADNI3: 0=No ; 1=Yes ; 2=N/A Scanner manufacturer is GE

    • ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • MALFUNC character Scanner Malfunction:

    • ADNI2: 1=Yes ; 0=No

    • ADNI3, ADNI4: 0=No ; 1=Yes

    Decoded Value: Yes

  • FLDSTRNGTH character Field Strength 1=1.5 Tesla ; 2=3 Tesla Decoded Value: Yes

  • ID numeric Record ID Range value: 6, ..., 176409

  • SITEID numeric Site ID Range value: 1, ..., 127

  • USERDATE User Create Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • USERDATE2 User Last Modify Date Date: YYY-MM-DD

  • UPDATE_STAMP POSIXct: YYY-MM-DD
